OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779563472
OL,3,CAlex Scott left out of England World
OL,4,CCup squad
OL,6,FGuernsey footballer Alex Scott has
OL,7,Ffailed to make it into Thomas Tuchel's
OL,8,F26-man England squad for the World Cup.
OL,10,FThe Bournemouth player was named in
OL,11,Fthe German's 55-man provisional group
OL,12,Flast week but will not be on the plane
OL,13,Fto the United States.
OL,15,FScott, 23, is yet to make an
OL,16,Fappearance for England at senior level
OL,17,Fbut was in the squad for the team's
OL,18,Ffinal World Cup qualifiers against
OL,19,FAlbania and Serbia in November.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
