OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779563472
OL,3,CAlex Scott left out of England World
OL,4,CCup squad
OL,6,FHe has, however, been an integral part
OL,7,Fof England's Under 21s setup, winning
OL,8,Fthe Euros last year.
OL,10,FAfter recovering from a meniscus tear
OL,11,Fin the 2024-2025 season, the
OL,12,Fmidfielder has also been a driving
OL,13,Fforce for Bournemouth this season as
OL,14,Fthey continue their last gasp push for
OL,15,FChampions League football.
OL,17,FScott has featured in every Premier
OL,18,FLeague game this campaign, scoring
OL,19,Fthree goals.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
