OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1779563472
OL,3,CAlex Scott left out of England World
OL,4,CCup squad
OL,6,FHe made 15 appearances for Guernsey FC
OL,7,Fin 2019-2020 before a three-year spell
OL,8,Fat Bristol City and a transfer to
OL,9,FBournemouth in 2023, and has since
OL,10,Fplayed 86 times for the club.
OL,12,FThe World Cup kicks off on 11 June
OL,13,Fwith the Three Lions opening their
OL,14,Fcampaign against Croatia six days
OL,15,Flater.
